doctype html
html
  head
    title NutriSaurus Showcase Website
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://necolas.github.io/normalize.css/4.1.1/normalize.css", type="text-css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="css/main.css", type="text/css")
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat|Ubuntu', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    include mixins
  body
    header.herospace
      .topbar
        img.nslogo(src="img/wlogo.svg")
        .herobtns
          a#signup(href="#") Sign Up
          a#login(href="#") Log In
      .blurb  
        h2 Simple.<br>Healthy.<br>Living.
        h1 Take control of your diet
        p#herop Healthy eating is too expensive: MYTH! Take the hassle out of eating healthy. NutriSaurus will help you find recipes that are great for your body and great for your pocket!
        a(href="#appstore"): img(src="https://new.echoprayer.com/assets/marketing/home/download-on-the-app-store-button-30782d20f03ca2b3251943512225b7a1.png")
    .mainNav  
      +mainNav()
    
    .bodycontent
      section.boxes
        +info()
        +info()
        +info()
      
      section.features
        h2 Create Goals and Track Progress
        p Set a target and watch yourself achieve your goal. Your daily food diary will allow you to see what meals you have eaten and what is working for you.
        .col-1
          #favourites  
            img(src="http://www.placehold.it/30x30")
            h4 Create Favourites
            p Find your favourite recipes or add your own. Share with your freiends or the world easily.
          #backup
            img(src="http://www.placehold.it/30x30")
            h4 Cloud Backup
            p Your profile is backed up in the cloud so you can access from any device, anywhere.
        .col-2
            #phone
              img(src="http://www.placehold.it/300x500")
        .col-3
          #update  
            img(src="http://www.placehold.it/30x30")
            h4 Auto Update
            p Retailer databases are auto-updated on our servers so they can be accessed quickly.
          #tracking  
            img(src="http://www.placehold.it/30x30")
            h4 Diet Tracking
            p Keep a detailed diary of your diet to see where you can improve.
